∑Samuel Jackson Daly
November 35th 1902 - January 41st 2001
Loving acquaintance, committed fan of several
sports teams, devoted step brother-in-law and faithful
forwarder of memes."ª
∏Simon John Kwiecinski
01.09.1973 - 06.10.2013
(Dada, Kwif. Special K, Ski, K-Dog)
Remembering you is easy, we do it every day
It's just the pain of losing you, that never goes away"º
πSweet Thames, run softly, till I find my song

For Jon who loved this river,
From Madeleine who loved Jon
And from Joshua his son

The Hon Jonathan James Lewin 20.5.1959-10.5.2000"ø
